message.body: Yo, are you still at the bar?
At the moment. How was the movie?
Good. Who you with? Are you at the honeys? We could be there in 20 minutes. How are you staying?
Are you "with" the honeys? How "long" are you stating?
I came with some dudes who promised honeys, but its not looking good here tonight.
I was planning on staying until 1ish
Okay then. I guess I'll just stay home. I'll talk to you soon!
We wouldn't be able to get there until 1:15-ish
